    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity under load. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension has been tightened with polyurethane bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining precise turn-in and lateral stability. While the exterior shows honest road wear, the mechanical synchronization and visceral throttle response remain top-tier.",
